  "All the solute has dissolved completely with none remaining": "",
  "The temperature and pressure are both changing simultaneously": "",
  "In a saturated solution at equilibrium, the rate of dissolving equals the rate of crystallization. Solute is constantly dissolving and re-crystallizing at equal rates.": "",
